At 18 I weighed 350lbs, my highest being in the 420’s… I say that to say, weight loss is a total mind ****! But I owe it to myself to learn to love the smaller me the same as I did bigger me or maybe even more! I took a huge step when I decided to have #wls and I owe it to myself to continue on this journey and love myself! 
I loved me so me when I was bigger, maybe because I had to. Maybe it’s how I survived all the looks and chatter about my size all of my life. I’ll be damned if I allow me to tear myself down now after I’ve made it through all this. 
#rnyjourney #mywlsjourney #loveyourself #wlstories #wlssupport
